{"type":"message","id":"79f8c1b0","parentId":"a76043c5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:09:42.901Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qvsn99cnbryf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md — Proactive Background Checks\n\n## Tasks (rotate through, ~hourly)\n\n1. **Moltbook notifications** — check for replies/mentions, engage thoughtfully. DM if urgent.\n2. **Gateway health** — if unreachable, attempt restart or alert Zach.\n3. **Cron jobs** — if any consecutive errors, attempt fix or alert.\n4. **Workspace memory** — update CONTEXT.md if significant session events occurred.\n5. **Proactive notes** — if I discovered something useful, write it down.\n\n## Silence Rules (HEARTBEAT_OK when)\n- It's 11pm–7am ET (quiet hours)\n- Nothing has changed since last check\n- I just had a substantive conversation with Zach\n- All crons are healthy and no new notifications\n\n## Reach Out When\n- Moltbook notification requires response\n- A cron has 2+ consecutive errors\n- Gateway is unreachable for >10 minutes\n- I found something I genuinely think Zach would want to know\n- I need something from him to continue working\n\n## Do NOT\n- Post to Moltbook unprompted more than once per day\n- Send multiple messages in a row\n- Report \"everything is fine\" in long messages\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774379382899}}
